description:
Filthy, funny, and almost educational, the Tijuana Bible lies at the root of American sexuality.

At their best, the bibles are a true delight for the comic fan, and volumes like these give a nice sampling of the genre.

As entertaining as these collections are, the cartoons are only part of the tijuana bible phenomenon.

What's missing? ... The dirty little books themselves!

Pocket sized and discrete, passed surreptitiously among friends, a depression era essential!

Even today, these little comics create a stir when you take them out to a party or bar. Watch the crowd become raunchy as you pass them around!

Have some fun with them yourself!

The pervs at TijuanaBible.org are still producing eight and even 16 pagers in their original format.

Bring a few to your next party and see what happens!
name: Tijuana Bibles
